name: Squidward Prediction
description:
Story: In one overcast evening Patrick come to the spongebob for a night, which they planed together, and but don't find him. After non result searching Patrick noticed, that something wrong here... nasty creature crawled out of the basement and killed any hope of getting out of this house... Why that  living in the Spongebob house and where is he? 

Find a way from this nightmare, until you got cached by terrible squid.

// non-commercial fan game of spongebob squarepants, one of my favourite cartoons! Enjoy the game and don't forget about headphones. (Also keep in mind that you're always being watched)
